text: Club Social y Deportivo Atlas de Guadalajara () is a Mexican football club. The club's home stadium is Estadio Jalisco in Guadalajara. ==Honors== *Primera División de México: 1 ::1950-51 *Copa México: 4 ::1945-46, 1949–50, 1961–62, 1967–68 *Campeón de Campeones: 4 ::1945-46, 1949–50, 1950–51, 1961–62 *Segunda División de México: 3 ::1954-55, 1971–72, 1978–79 *Amateur Era Occidental League Championships: 5 ::1917-21, 1935–36 ===Friendly International tournaments=== *Copa Marlboro: 1 ::1990 *Copa Cuadrangular: 2 ::2010, 2011 ==References== Category:Mexican football clubs Category:Guadalajara Category:1916 establishments in Mexico
title: Atlas F.C.
